<li>Integration of a complex regulatory cascade involving the SirA / BarA and Csr global regulatory systems that controls expression of the Salmonella SPI-1 and SPI-2 virulence regulons through HilD Luary C. Martínez1 , Helen Yakhnin2 , Martha I. Camacho3 , Dimitris Georgellis3 , Paul Babitzke2 , José L. Puente1 , and Víctor H. Bustamante1 , * 1Departamento de Microbiología Molecular , Instituto de Biotecnología , Universidad Nacional Autónoma de México .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21518393" target="_blank">21518393</a>]<br></li>
